snippet.title: Ectoplasm Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Step into the chilling world of paranormal investigation.
Gather crucial information from a haunted location using specialized equipment, all while staying one step ahead of the ghost.
Experience the psychological horror alone or in a team of up to 4 players.
